\item 2 x Intel Xeon E5620 Processor 2.4 GHz processor (264 €)[160 W]%ya los dos
\item 48GB DDR3 ECC Registered (300 €)
\item 1 x Mellanox ConnectX-2 MHQH19B-XTR Infiniband (211 €)
\end{enumerate}\vspace{0.1in}


