\begin{enumerate}
\item 1 x Supermicro 7046GT-TRF SuperServer (1.616 €)[32.7 kg][452x178x673 mm][1400 W high-efficiency]
\item 2 x Intel Xeon E5620 Processor 2.4 GHz processor (264 €)
\item 16 nodos: 4x NVIDIA Quadro K1200 GPUs (4 x 180 €)
\item 5 nodos: 4x NVIDIA Quadro K2200 GPUs (4 x 500 €)
\item 2 nodo: 4x NVIDIA Tesla M40 GPUs (4 x 2648 €)
\item 2 nodo: 4x NVIDIA Tesla M60 GPUs (4 x 6471 €)
